1. BP_Healthcomponent contains health and stamina

2. Regen health function is inside the BP_BaseCharacter blueprint (base). Adjust the apply damage from -1.0 or any negative number to speed or slow regen.

3. To deal stamina damage or other types of stat damage, look at the function "On Damage Taken" inside the BP_BaseCharacter. And Check the instigator function
of player and bot at the end of the graph.

4. If you need to modify hp, max hp, stamina, and max stamina or add new stats like mana, you need to go into BP_Healthcomponent, the blueprint itself in blueprints
-> healthcomponent

It is NOT located in bp_basecharacter

5. 
